  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-language SDK support (TypeScript, Python, Go, .NET, Java, YAML)",
    "Complete coverage of AWS services and resources",
    "Enhanced multi-region support — manage resources across regions without multiple provider configs",
    "Serverless functions via aws.lambda.CallbackFunction for native code-to-Lambda conversion",
    "IAM role chaining and OIDC/WebIdentity authentication",
    "Default tags propagation across all resources",
    "Pulumi ESC integration for dynamic credential management",
    "Type-safe resource definitions with full AWS API coverage"
  ],
